Hi,

h4. Test Code

app.js
{code}
var tabGroup = Titanium.UI.createTabGroup({});
 
var win1 = Titanium.UI.createWindow({
    backgroundColor: 'green',
    //tabBarHidden: true
});
 
var tab1 = Titanium.UI.createTab({
    window: win1
});
 
tabGroup.addTab(tab1);
tabGroup.open();
{code}

h4. Problem Description

Custom titanium_tabgroup.xml work since Ti SDK 2.X.X but it doesnâ€™t work for Ti SDK 3.X.X. In the project directory "Project_Name/platform/android/res/layout/", we use the titanium_tabgroup.xml file.

Reference link: https://developer.appcelerator.com/question/127317/hide-tab-bar-on-android

h4. Steps to reproduce

- Create a simple classic project
- Update app.js with test code
- Add titanium_tabgroup.xml file in "Project_Name/platform/android/res/layout/" directory
- Run on android device

Screenshot of titanium_tabgroup.xml file directory: http://oi62.tinypic.com/20b093k.jpg
